msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Sinclair - ZX Spectrum (Fuse)"
msgstr "Sinclair - ZX Spectrum (Fuse)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Fuse (the Free Unix Spectrum Emulator) was originally a ZX Spectrum emulator for Unix. It has since been ported to Mac OS X, Windows, the Wii, AmigaOS and MorphOS."
msgstr "Fuse (Free Unix Spectrum Emulator) byl původně emulátor ZX Spectrum pro Unix. Od té doby byl portován na Mac OS X, Windows, Wii, AmigaOS a MorphOS."

